description:
GStreamer 1.26 open-source multimedia framework is now available for download with H.266 Versatile Video Coding (VVC) codec support, as well as many other changes. Here's what's new!

The post GStreamer 1.26 Open-Source Multimedia Framework Released, Here’s What’s New appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: GStreamer 1.26 Open-Source Multimedia Framework Released, Here’s What’s New
